{"tid":2388458,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"櫃員機盜竊案 28歲男警員被捕 被控4宗罪 律政司拖足2年才決定落案起訴 二月四日東區法院提堂","createTime":"2021-01-31T06:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T04:04:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3f1166eed7a0718075c792caec4312ddef9d9bc5","tid":2388458,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:53:15.000Z","msg":"警方於審視一宗發生於2017年2月的銀行櫃員機盜竊案件期間，懷疑一名警員偽造調查文件，上周四(28/1)於上水區拘捕該名28歲男警員，他已被停職。被捕警員已被控以一項「公職人員行為失當」罪及三項「偽造文書」罪，案件將於二月四日在東區裁判法院提堂，案件交由灣仔警區重案組接手調查。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，被捕警員隸屬灣仔警區，2017年為灣仔區刑事調查隊隊員，案發時撰寫虛假的調查報告，並冒充案件主管簽名作實，訛稱一宗櫃員機盜竊案的一名受害人已經獲銀行賠償，事件其後於2018年被人悉破。灣仔重案組接收調查後不久便快速破案，並向律政司諮詢法律意見，但律政司拖足2年才決定落案起訴涉案警員。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210131/MW7MHFEI7ZCQNMJZQNZKME32T4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210131%2FMW7MHFEI7ZCQNMJZQNZKME32T4%2F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWgoJw9ynFthkhoOYQBA%2BRXM%3D&h=0efd42ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210131%2FMW7MHFEI7ZCQNMJZQNZKME32T4%2F&h=7457ea50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210131/MW7MHFEI7ZCQNMJZQNZKME32T4/</a>"},{"pid":"556dfe0ff871c6da918fab8386cf6bdbf6ec9ee7","tid":2388458,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"